        "text_yJNrKP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h1><strong>Share Mindfulness. Earn Rewards.</strong></h1><p>Join the Breathelet Affiliate Program and help others live calmer, more focused lives — while earning commissions for every sale.</p><h3>💫 About Breathelet</h3><p>At <strong>Breathelet</strong>, we believe mindfulness should feel effortless. Our minimalist, adjustable bracelet uses gentle, spontaneous vibrations to remind you to pause, breathe, and refocus — helping you build mindfulness and balance into your daily routine.When you become an affiliate, you’re not just promoting a product — you’re sharing a mindful lifestyle that truly makes a difference.</p><h3>🌸 Who Can Join</h3><p>If you believe in mindfulness, personal growth, and intentional living — you’re a perfect fit. Whether you’re a content creator, yoga instructor, wellness coach, or simply someone who loves inspiring others, you’re welcome in our community.</p><h3>✨ How It Works</h3><ol><li><strong>Apply</strong> to join the Breathelet Affiliate Program.</li><li><strong>Share</strong> your unique link with your audience through social media, blogs, or videos.</li><li><strong>Earn</strong> commissions on every sale made through your link.</li></ol><p>It’s that simple — share calm, earn income, and help others breathe a little easier.</p><h3>❤️ Let’s Grow Together</h3><p>Be part of a movement that spreads mindfulness and balance — one breath at a time.<a href=\"https://ui.awin.com/express-signup/en/awin/121054/b4de8bf0-d505-4bae-8110-16c33b47822b?t=zFuiyEuvWzRDom5d9UfMVLvZZ-c9AxpVaBcpvgEGjHU\" title=\"https://ui.awin.com/express-signup/en/awin/121054/b4de8bf0-d505-4bae-8110-16c33b47822b?t=zFuiyEuvWzRDom5d9UfMVLvZZ-c9AxpVaBcpvgEGjHU\">👉 <strong>Apply now to become a Breathelet Affiliate</strong></a> and start turning calm into commissions.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
